{"issue_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rails/rails/issues/7771", "repo": "rails", "body": "My concern is the number of steps it takes to get to a blank project. Now instead of just removing one file, I need to remove a controller, view directory, and the routes?\n\nWhat if we generate no additional files, and simply have one line in the routes file:\n\n```ruby\nroot to: welcome_aboard\n```\n\nThis could be a rack handler which responds with the dynamic content internally (like the existing `/rails/info/properties` path works).", "_id": {"$oid": "523dcb5dbd354364b900a140"}, "issue_id": 7771, "url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rails/rails/issues/comments/8943828", "html_url": "https://github.com/rails/rails/pull/7771#issuecomment-8943828", "updated_at": "2012-09-27T17:07:33Z", "user": {"subscriptions_url": "https://api.github.com/users/ryanb/subscriptions", "events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/ryanb/events{/privacy}", "repos_url": "https://api.github.com/users/ryanb/repos", "gists_url": "https://api.github.com/users/ryanb/gists{/gist_id}", "url": "https://api.github.com/users/ryanb", "login": "ryanb", "gravatar_id": "8dbf316d36ff66aad4869a4fc3cfbd37", "html_url": "https://github.com/ryanb", "following_url": "https://api.github.com/users/ryanb/following{/other_user}", "received_events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/ryanb/received_events", "organizations_url": "https://api.github.com/users/ryanb/orgs", "avatar_url": "https://1.gravatar.com/avatar/8dbf316d36ff66aad4869a4fc3cfbd37?d=https%3A%2F%2Fidenticons.github.com%2Fbd4c9ab730f5513206b999ec0d90d1fb.png", "starred_url": "https://api.github.com/users/ryanb/starred{/owner}{/repo}", "id": 161, "followers_url": "https://api.github.com/users/ryanb/followers", "type": "User"}, "created_at": "2012-09-27T17:06:22Z", "id": 8943828, "owner": "rails"}
